verbose_text: Importantly, this association between high WNT6 mRNA levels and poor prognosis in GBM patients was further validated in 3 additional independent datasets : Freije (n = 59) XREF_BIBR, Gravendeel (n = 159) XREF_BIBR and Vital (n = 26) XREF_BIBR datasets (p = 0.006, p = 0.029, p = 0.02, respectively; Figure XREF_FIG B-D).
